verbose_text: Moreover, we also found that the upregulation of Cav1 contributed to the DHA mediated p53 activation and the downregulation of the redox enzyme, NAD (P) H : quinone oxidoreductase 1 (NQO1), which have been reported to contribute to the activation of the cell death pathway.
